location_details: This is a toilet of Richmond Cafe. You might buy some dishes or items to enter the toilet.
This toilet is in museum and has to pay for the entry fee for the however the toilet use is free . Toilet is in good condition and is frequently cleaned.

this toilet is owned and managed by Mahalaxmi Temple Management committee. This toilet is not public one however, it is accessible for those who wants to visit temple. Not categorized as a public toilet one it is in access for general people.

This toilet owned by the municipality has been operated by Deula's since a long time. There are separate toilets for male and female however, the condition of toilets are not good as most of them are lacking door .
This public toilet is in access of everyone trying to visit the patan durbar square. this toilet is not accessible for everyone . the condition of toilet is not good as it is not well cleaned

this toilet is located in sasto bazar of dhaugal . this toilet has been in operation since a long time . condition of toilet i not so good as there is scarcity of water. it is not in access of disable people also.
This toilet is being operated by patan hospital and is in access of common people in case of emergency for them. this toilet has separate cubical for male and female and is cleaned time and again
